      "side": 1,
      "message": "isOnMaster will return false, which will return IgnoreResultsFileErr, which means processResult [1] will *not* add it to the list of processed files, which means it will be re-ingested on the next time we poll for missed data (every 20-60 minutes).\n\n[1] https://github.com/google/skia-buildbot/blob/aae8a72948a396fed14fe47e50bca2c5939aa03e/go/ingestion/ingestion.go#L216",
